00:06:55.200 --> 00:06:56.000
Speak up.

00:06:56.480 --> 00:06:57.680
Where is the Xuanzhu Jade?

00:06:58.400 --> 00:07:00.080
I don't know any Xuanzhu Jade.

00:07:03.557 --> 00:07:06.517
I saw the Xuanzhu Jade on you
with my own eyes.

00:07:09.440 --> 00:07:10.720
Don't try to trick me.

00:07:11.560 --> 00:07:13.600
I have ways to make you suffer.

00:07:14.000 --> 00:07:16.080
If you tell me
where the Xuanzhu Jade is.

00:07:16.080 --> 00:07:17.800
I don't know anything about it.

00:07:18.440 --> 00:07:19.320
If you don't talk,

00:07:20.600 --> 00:07:22.200
you must die.

00:07:38.680 --> 00:07:40.320
(Xuanzhu Jade is really inside you.)

00:07:42.120 --> 00:07:43.560
You're a Wangshu Vessel.

00:07:44.920 --> 00:07:46.880
(I really have the Xuanzhu Jade
inside me?)

00:07:47.360 --> 00:07:48.240
(Could this be why)

00:07:48.720 --> 00:07:50.920
(I was born with red hair?)

00:07:53.000 --> 00:07:54.000
(Great.)

00:07:58.920 --> 00:07:59.840
What are you trying to do?

00:08:00.040 --> 00:08:01.200
I'll use you as a sacrifice.

00:08:01.200 --> 00:08:01.720
Let go.

00:08:01.720 --> 00:08:02.880
To save my clan.

00:08:06.840 --> 00:08:07.640
(What's going on?)

00:08:24.160 --> 00:08:24.960
Impossible.

00:08:25.480 --> 00:08:27.040
You clearly have
the Xuanzhu Jade on you.

00:08:27.560 --> 00:08:28.640
Why won't it return?

00:08:56.000 --> 00:08:57.040
(How come?)

00:08:58.440 --> 00:08:59.600
(What is this?)

00:09:07.640 --> 00:09:09.480
(All things return to their place.)

00:09:09.480 --> 00:09:11.600
(To offer me a heart,)

00:09:11.600 --> 00:09:13.640
(it must be a willing sacrifice,)

00:09:14.040 --> 00:09:16.040
(so that the jade could return
to its place.)

00:09:25.440 --> 00:09:26.480
I can

00:09:26.680 --> 00:09:27.800
offer myself willingly.

00:09:29.080 --> 00:09:31.120
You want the Xuanzhu Jade
inside my body, don't you?

00:09:32.000 --> 00:09:32.920
How about

00:09:33.640 --> 00:09:34.840
we make a deal?

00:09:36.320 --> 00:09:37.760
Who do you think you are

00:09:40.480 --> 00:09:42.280
to bargain with me?

00:09:42.760 --> 00:09:44.560
Didn't you just try?

00:09:44.880 --> 00:09:46.880
Sacrifice needs my consent.

00:09:51.240 --> 00:09:52.520
My entire family was massacred.

00:09:53.720 --> 00:09:55.120
I was nearly burnt
in a sacrificial rite.

00:09:55.920 --> 00:09:57.200
I will not die in peace

00:09:57.200 --> 00:09:58.440
until I avenge them.

00:09:59.400 --> 00:10:01.000
If you help me get revenge,

00:10:01.440 --> 00:10:02.640
I'll sacrifice myself willingly

00:10:02.960 --> 00:10:04.280
and let the Xuanzhu Jade return.

00:10:08.280 --> 00:10:10.240
I don't make deals with lowly humans.

00:10:35.120 --> 00:10:36.120
Mu Lingxue.

00:10:37.400 --> 00:10:38.800
Even if you have to kneel,

00:10:40.280 --> 00:10:42.080
you must survive.

00:10:52.820 --> 00:10:56.300
(On the full moon night, human and deity
combine to make a Twin-soul Contract.)

